{{nihongo|'''Lagunasia'''|ラグナシア|Ragunashia}} is an [[amusement park]] in [[Gamagōri, Aichi]], Japan. It is home to the Aqua Wind, Pirates' Blast and Stellar roller coasters. The park was also the first [[Magiquest]] live role playing game location outside of the United States.{{cn|date=December 2015}}

Lagunasia was opened on April 25, 2002. The construction of the amusement park is located in the Laguna Gamagōri, a resort which was a renewal project around the coast of Gamagōri city.

